<p class="ayah 45-3" id="3" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٲتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the heavens</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْأَرْضِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the earth</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَأَيَـٰتٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">surely (are) Signs</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِّلْمُؤْمِنِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for the believers.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>3<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
